ENH: updates to plot_matrix

- Change argument ax to axes, for consistency with other
  plotting functions

- Enable to control figure size (the goal being to minimize usage of
  matplotlib in examples)

- Better axes padding with colobar

- Title positioning and scaling

- Add to whats_new and module reference

- Separate out tests in their own file (one test file per module file)
Plot_matrix accessible from plotting and added cmap default

FIX: Documentation build error with sphinx

- Pattern not found fix in region extraction

add group information

-updates sklearn.cross_validation to sklearn.model_selection
-adds group label argument for cross validation schemes accepting labels
such as LeaveOneGroupOut()
